pages.strategyCreate.step1.title: Create Strategy
pages.strategyCreate.step1.section2.stra: Tokens acquired in a buy order become automatically available to trade in the linked sell order, and vice versa.
An irreversible buy or sell order at a predefined price or range.
pages.strategyCreate.step1.tooltips.tool: Select the Base token for the pair
Select the Quote token for the pair (i.e. when selecting USDC, all rates would be denominated in USDC)

Selecting the tokens you would like to create a strategy for.
Buy or Sell token (also called Base token) is the token you would like to buy or sell in the strategy.
With token (also called Quote token) is the token you would denominate the rates in.

Define the price you are willing to sell {{buyToken}} at. Make sure the price is in {{sellToken}} tokens.
Note: this amount will re-fill once the "Sell" order is used by traders.
The amount of {{sellToken}} tokens you would like to use in order to buy {{buyToken}}.
Note: this amount will re-fill once the "Buy" order is used by traders.
The amount of {{buyToken}} tokens you would like to sell.
